{
  "stem": "1363.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't know whether I was official or not, because once we were out of the gate, he didn't know I got up, I went straight, and he didn't know whether I belonged to the 23, 24, or not.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was no problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we walked quite a bit to get to a certain protected house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, because I didn't have any official papers-- official, meaning Wallenberg papers, I had to stay in the building, instead of going down to the cellar.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But, anybody who was paying for it, they had to go down the cellar because we got the bombs constantly.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was up on the top floor, third floor, in that particular building, on the 6th of January.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So, we arrived there on December.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Food I got from them, but I had to take it upstairs or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can't recall that food business there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I only know that I had-- I was up there, not in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And on the 6th of January, we had a sort of a carpet bombing, where I don't know whether the Americans, the English, or the Russians were bombarding Budapest in a heavy way.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was on the third floor, and I huddled into a corner because I was afraid, when are we going to cop the bomb.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And sure enough, we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was on my own on that third floor, and the bomb went through the staircase.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when I opened up my eyes, the dust.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when the dust cleared itself, it was the air, the sky.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Somehow or other, I got down, and the whole house was evacuated, because that was-- they couldn't have-- have us there anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
